      <title>Meta 推出非定制广告以缓解欧盟的担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/meta-unveils-less-targeted-ads-to-allay-eu-regulators-concerns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Meta Platforms Inc. 正在撤回针对欧洲用户的定向广告，以解决欧盟对该公司订阅模式的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/meta-unveils-less-targeted-ads-to-allay-eu-regulators-concerns</guid>
